{"prompt": "Generate a website for a sustainable fashion brand. The website should be vibrant and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Evergreen Threads</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f4f4;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: #e52b50; /* Vibrant Red */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #cc0000 3px solid;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n        nav {\n            background: #cc0000; /* Slightly darker red */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        nav ul {\n            padding: 0;\n            list-style: none;\n        }\n        nav ul li {\n            display: inline;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: #fff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #f4f4f4;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background: #e52b50; /* Vibrant Red */\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .hero h2 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            line-height: 1.2;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n        }\n        .hero .btn {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background: #fff;\n            color: #e52b50;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .hero .btn:hover {\n            background: #f4f4f4;\n            color: #cc0000;\n        }\n        .features {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .features h3 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: #e52b50;\n        }\n        .feature-item {\n            width: 30%;\n            float: left;\n            margin: 1.5%;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background: #fff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n        }\n        .feature-item h4 {\n            color: #e52b50;\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n        }\n        .feature-item img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .cta {\n            background: #cc0000;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 50px 0;\n        }\n        .cta h3 {\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .cta p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .cta .btn {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background: #fff;\n            color: #cc0000;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .cta .btn:hover {\n            background: #f4f4f4;\n            color: #e52b50;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background: #333;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        .clearfix::after {\n            content: \"\";\n            clear: both;\n            display: table;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 95%;\n            }\n            .feature-item {\n                width: 90%;\n                float: none;\n                margin: 20px auto;\n            }\n            .hero h2 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.1em;\n            }\n            nav ul li {\n                display: block;\n                margin: 10px 0;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Evergreen Threads</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"#about\">About Us</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#products\">Our Products</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#sustainability\">Sustainability</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Style with a Conscience</h2>\n            <p>Discover fashion that feels good and does good.</p>\n            <a href=\"#products\" class=\"btn\">Shop Our Collection</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"features container\"