tps://via.placeholder.com/300x200/cc0000/ffffff?text=Trousers\" alt=\"Relaxed Trouser\">\n            <p>Comfortable and stylish, crafted from recycled linen blend.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"feature-item\">\n            <h4>The Versatile Dress</h4>\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/e52b50/ffffff?text=Dress\" alt=\"Versatile Dress\">\n            <p>Effortlessly chic, made from Tencel\u2122 Lyocell.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"cta\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Join the Sustainable Fashion Movement</h3>\n            <p>Ready to make a difference with your wardrobe? Explore our collection and be part of the change.</p>\n            <a href=\"mailto:info@evergreenthreads.com\" class=\"btn\">Get In Touch</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Evergreen Threads. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}